```plantuml
@startuml kryptokrauts_ae-prediction-cards
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Frontend" as FE {
  rectangle "WalletClient.ts" as WalletClient #lightgoldenrodyellow
  rectangle "PredictionCards.api.ts" as PredictionAPI #lightgoldenrodyellow
  rectangle "state.ts" as State #lightgoldenrodyellow
}

rectangle "Aeternity Blockchain" as Blockchain #mistyrose {
  rectangle "PredictionCards\nSmart Contract" as Contract #palegreen
}

rectangle "process-prediction-\nservice" as PredictionService #lightsteelblue

rectangle "oracle-service" as OracleService #lightyellow

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> FE

' Frontend interactions
FE <--> WalletClient : Connect to wallet\nManage account data
FE <--> PredictionAPI : Interact with smart contract\ncreate predictions, rent NFTs, claim rewards
FE <--> State : Manage app state\n(wallet connection)
PredictionAPI <--> Blockchain : Smart contract calls\nvia aepp-sdk-js

' Blockchain interactions
Blockchain <--> OracleService : Oracle interactions\nregister, query, respond
Blockchain <--> PredictionService : Monitor predictions\ntrigger oracle queries

' Backend services interactions
PredictionService --> Blockchain : Check for predictions\nwith state "CLOSED"
PredictionService --> Contract : Trigger oracle query\nask_for_winning_option
Blockchain --> PredictionService : Oracle response\nprocess_oracle_response

OracleService --> Blockchain : Respond to queries\nwith price outcome
OracleService --> OracleService : Fetch price data\nfrom external API

@enduml
```